-- Xolo - Nationwide online accounting service for freelancers
('Xolo', 'Accounting', 'All-in-one online accounting service for freelancers (autónomos) in Spain. Formerly known as LeapIN. Offers company registration, invoicing, tax compliance, and accounting management entirely online with English-speaking support. Services include autónomo registration in Hacienda and Social Security within 24 hours, invoice creation and management, expense tracking with deductible optimization, quarterly tax filings, and annual Renta declaration. Each client is assigned a dedicated expert accountant for personalized service. Ideal for digital nomads, remote workers, and international freelancers needing English-language support for Spanish tax and accounting obligations. Nationwide coverage with fully online service delivery.', 'Nationwide online service', 'Madrid', 'Madrid', NULL, NULL, 'https://www.xolo.io/es-en', true, false, true, false, NOW(), NOW());
